<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.400715>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Phortica (Ashima) yalianae sp. nov. ι male. (a) arista; (b) epandriumι cercus and surstylus (lateral view); (c) surstylus (inner view); (d) hypandriumι parameres and gonopods (ventral view); (e) hypandriumι gonopodsι paramereι aedeagus and aedeagal apodeme (lateral view). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/400715/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.400714>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Phortica (Ashima) libo sp. nov. ι male. (a) arista; (b) epandrium (epand) ι cercus (cerc) and surstylus (sur) (lateral view); (c) surstylus (inner view); (d) hypandrium (hypd) ι parameres (pm) and gonopods (gon) (ventral view); (e) hypandriumι gonopodsι paramereι aedeagus (ade) and aedeagal apodeme (aed a) (lateral view). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/400714/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.400716>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Phortica (Ashima) yiqini sp. nov. ι male. (a) arista; (b) epandriumι cercus and surstylus (lateral view); (c) surstylus (inner view); (d) hypandriumι parameres and gonopods (ventral view); (e) hypandriumι gonopodsι paramereι aedeagus and aedeagal apodeme (lateral view). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
